      "description": "We are pleased to present an automotive specimen of the highest caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, having been curated with rigorous attention to detail and mechanical preservation. Every surface and component reflects a standard of excellence that transcends the typical pre-owned market, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original debut. For the discerning individual seeking a benchmark-level acquisition, this represents a rare opportunity to secure a vehicle of unrivaled integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
