    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty in person\u2014it's honestly like stepping back in time to the day it was first bought! It\u2019s been pampered its whole life, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and there isn't a single blemish to be found. It still has that fresh 'new car' smell and drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat and show you why this is the perfect ride for you!",
